casebody.data:
Layton, Respondent, v. Brady, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 14, 1892.) Action by R. C. Layton against Patrick Brady.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. See 20 N. Y. Supp. 534.
